<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mentor Application Update - Reserva FTIC</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9b00 0%, #0b8200 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .status-submitted {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            color: #1976d2;
        }
        .status-approved {
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            color: #2e7d32;
        }
        .status-rejected {
            background-color: #ffebee;
            color: #c62828;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #0d9b00;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9b00 0%, #0b8200 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Reserva FTIC</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{ user.firstName }},</p>
            
            {% if status == 'submitted' %}
                <h2>Your Mentor Application Has Been Submitted</h2>
                <div class="status-badge status-submitted">Submitted</div>
                
                <p>Thank you for applying to become a mentor at Reserva FTIC! We have received your application and it is now under review.</p>
                
                <div class="info-box">
                    <strong>Application ID:</strong> #{{ applicationId }}<br>
                    <strong>Status:</strong> Pending Review
                </div>
                
                <p>Our team will carefully review your qualifications and experience. You will receive another email once a decision has been made.</p>
                
                <p>What happens next?</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Our Super Admin will review your application</li>
                    <li>You may be contacted for additional information if needed</li>
                    <li>You will receive an email notification once approved or if additional information is required</li>
                </ul>
                
            {% elseif status == 'approved' %}
                <h2>Congratulations! Your Application Has Been Approved</h2>
                <div class="status-badge status-approved">Approved</div>
                
                <p>Great news! Your mentor application has been reviewed and approved by our team.</p>
                
                <div class="info-box">
                    <strong>Application ID:</strong> #{{ applicationId }}<br>
                    <strong>Status:</strong> Approved
                </div>
                
                <p>You are now officially a mentor at Reserva FTIC! You can start accepting mentoring requests from students.</p>
                
                <p>What's next?</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your mentor profile is now active</li>
                    <li>Students can now view your profile and request mentoring sessions</li>
                    <li>You will receive notifications when students request your guidance</li>
                </ul>
                
            {% elseif status == 'rejected' %}
                <h2>Update on Your Mentor Application</h2>
                <div class="status-badge status-rejected">Not Approved</div>
                
                <p>We have reviewed your mentor application and unfortunately, we are unable to approve it at this time.</p>
                
                <div class="info-box">
                    <strong>Application ID:</strong> #{{ applicationId }}<br>
                    <strong>Status:</strong> Not Approved
                    {% if reason %}<br><strong>Reason:</strong> {{ reason }}{% endif %}
                </div>
                
                {% if reason %}
                    <p><strong>Feedback:</strong> {{ reason }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                
                <p>You are welcome to reapply in the future if your qualifications change. We encourage you to continue developing your expertise and consider applying again.</p>
                
            {% endif %}
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Reserva FTIC Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated email from Reserva FTIC. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Reserva FTIC. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
